--- FRESH STARDUST UPDATE ---
An update focusing on extra flavor, quality of life, and aesthetic upgrades.

--- Additions 
+ GUN REWORKS AND UPGRADES!: All unique guns have been upgraded. All vanilla and Starburst guns now have new sprites, animations, and bullet casings where applicable! (Thanks to Nitrosteel for teaching me how.) Certain gun alt-fires have been converted into an "ammo-swap" variant, giving the primary fire a new projectile or properties, rather than a direct alt-fire.
# Gun Alt-Fires Changed
## Vanilla
+ Iron Assault Rifle
+ Titanium Sniper
+ Hunter Rifle
+ Space Plasma Rifle (New Alt: Room Clear Mode)
+ Neo Tommy Gun (New Alt: Spray-N-Pray)
+ Neo Shotgun (New Alt: Plasma Mines)
+ Ex Machina (New Alt: WP Incindiary Rocket)
## Starburst
+ Leaf Blower
+ Foundry Launcher
+ Aurium Scoped Rifle
+ Heartwood Carbine (New Alt)
+ Blue Ice Shotgun (New Alt: Solidify/Vaporize)
+ Kaigun (New Alt: Shipbreaker)

+ EXPLORER'S JOURNAL AND COLLECTIONS!: New collections have been added to the game, they can be found in the new Explorer's Journal item. Obtained from your ship or crafted from a Foraging Table/Agricultural Station, can also found on Quickbar. It includes further info on the items and descriptions describing the category itself. These should hopefully grant further insight into what this mod has to offer.
